snippet.title: Amber Heard Back in Aquaman 2 Confirmed?
snippet.description:
In today's video we are going to discuss about is amber heard back in Aquaman 2. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

The world saw Amber Heard play the role of ‘Mera’ in the 2018 fantasy-thriller movie Aquaman. Her character was loved by one and all! As the second addition to the series, Aquaman 2 was announced, rumours started doing rounds that Amber Heard is no longer part of the movie franchise. But recent developments have something else to say!
